I had the honor to create the art for another beer collaboration with @blackflagbrewingco and we are celebrating the release at @luckybirdtattoo this Saturday with a fun flash day! Read below with details from @luckybirdtattoo 👇

🍻 SATURDAY, 7/8 @ 11-7pm 🍻
BFB x LBT Tattoo Flash Day!!

This is our 2nd annual beer collaboration with the amazing team at @blackflagbrewingco being released this July 8th weekend!  The Tattooed Brew is our follow-up release to our 2022 collaboration beer, Lucky Island TIPA.  Lucky Bird owner and artist Parry Chotipradit created one of Black Flag Brewery's most unique beer labels to date, coming up with the name and concept to incorporate the collaboration between the tattoo and craft beer world. Pulling from the sideshows of yesteryear, Parry deftly blended his unique style and color palette into a label that represents how both Lucky Bird and Black Flag have been pushing the envelope outside of established norms and blazing new trails together and separately for years now. We’re excited to bring you THE TATTOOED BREW across Maryland starting July 7th!

THE TATTOOED BREW
Hazy IPA - 7% ABV
$16.00/4pk

THE TATTOOED BREW - This 7% Hazy IPA features Mosaic, Simcoe, and Strata hops along with our traditional flaked oat and yeast build to bring you a tropical yet almost silky quality to the beer. Mango, pithy Tangerine, and a hint of stonefruit pop to the front of this wonder-in-a-glass. 

• Available Friday, 7/7 on draft and in cans to-go in the taproom at Black Flag Brewing Company

• Available Saturday, 7/8 for all tattooed clients at Lucky Bird Tattoo's Tattoo Flash Day! 

🤙🏼🍻😁 

For more info, visit www.luckybirdtattoo.com

Since most people work on Fridays, we decided this year to skip Friday the 13th and celebrate Saturday the 14th!  Come join us at Lucky Bird Tattoo for our Halloween Tattoo Flash Day event from 11am-7pm!  It's definitely going to be an amazing Halloween day because we've got 8 of our talented tattoo artists lined up for some seriously spooky tattoos. 

This event will be walk-ins only on a first come, first served basis. There will be plenty of spooky, Halloween themed flash tattoo designs available on the day of the event. Our staff will try to leak some sneak peeks of these designs leading up to the 14th but we always love the suspense of curiosity and anticipation!

As if that wasn't enough, we'll also have live music from The Fuses, our friends at  @thirdeyecomics will have a booth set up and giving away free comic books and swag, and amazing tacos and burgers from the @breakingtheborders food truck. To complete the experience, we’ll have trick-or-treat gift bags with some cute prizes for guests getting tattooed. Don't miss out on the fun!

Since most people work on Fridays, we decided this year to skip Friday the 13th and celebrate Saturday the 14th!  Come join us @luckybirdtattoo for our Halloween Tattoo Flash Day event from 11am-7pm!  It’s definitely going to be an amazing Halloween day because we’ve got 10 of our talented tattoo artists lined up for some seriously spooky tattoos with over 10 sheets of flash designs to choose from!

As if that wasn’t enough, we’ll also have live music from The Fuses, our talented friends from Third Eye Comics will have a booth set up giving away free comic books and awesome swag, and mouthwatering tacos and juicy burgers from the Breaking the Borders food truck.  And what Halloween celebration would be complete without a little trick-or-treat!? In addition to all the fantastic festivities, the first 50 guests who choose to get tattooed at the event will receive a special trick-or-treat gift bag filled with exciting prizes and candy! But wait, there’s more, because hidden within 5 of these trick bags lies an extra special surprise - a Lucky Bird Tattoo GIFT CARD! That’s right, you just might be one of the lucky few who will receive this unexpected treat. And to ensure that every unforgettable moment is captured, we’ve set up a brand new photo area where you can snap selfies and immortalize your experience. So mark your calendars and make sure you’re there to join in the fun with us!

This event will be walk-ins only on a first come, first served basis. There will be plenty of spooky, Halloween themed flash tattoo designs available on the day of the event. Our staff will try to leak some sneak peeks of these designs leading up to the 14th but we always love the suspense of curiosity and anticipation!  Come join us for a fantastic event! Enjoy tasty food, live music, comic books, exciting games, and incredible tattoos! We’ll also have an exclusive 1” enamel bird pins, Halloween bird stickers, candy, and other goodies. Don’t forget to save the date and come have a spooky time with us! www.luckybirdtattoo.com
